sequenceDiagram
    participant ML as ML Application
    participant ONLINE as Feature Server (Online)
    participant OFFLINE as Feature Server (Offline)
    participant REG as Registry Service
    participant TRANS as Transformation Service
    participant ONLINEDB as Online Store (Redis/PostgreSQL)
    participant OFFLINEDB as Offline Store (BigQuery/Snowflake)
    participant STREAM as Stream Processing App
    participant CRON as User/CronJob

    Note over ML,ONLINEDB: Flow 1: Real-Time Feature Retrieval
    ML->>+ONLINE: GET /get-online-features (HTTP:80, Optional Bearer)
    ONLINE->>+REG: Get Feature Metadata (gRPC:6570)
    REG-->>-ONLINE: Feature Definitions
    ONLINE->>+ONLINEDB: Read Features (Redis:6379/PostgreSQL:5432, TLS Optional)
    ONLINEDB-->>-ONLINE: Feature Values
    ONLINE->>+TRANS: Execute Transformations (gRPC:6569)
    TRANS-->>-ONLINE: Transformed Features
    ONLINE-->>-ML: Feature Response

    Note over ML,OFFLINEDB: Flow 2: Historical Feature Retrieval
    ML->>+OFFLINE: GET Historical Features (HTTP:8815, Optional Bearer)
    OFFLINE->>+REG: Get Feature Metadata (gRPC:6570)
    REG-->>-OFFLINE: Feature Definitions
    OFFLINE->>+OFFLINEDB: Query Historical Features (HTTPS:443, TLS 1.2+, Cloud IAM)
    OFFLINEDB-->>-OFFLINE: Historical Data
    OFFLINE-->>-ML: Historical Features

    Note over CRON,ONLINEDB: Flow 3: Feature Materialization
    CRON->>+ONLINE: POST /materialize (HTTP:80, Bearer Token)
    ONLINE->>+OFFLINEDB: Read Features (HTTPS:443, TLS 1.2+, Cloud IAM)
    OFFLINEDB-->>-ONLINE: Feature Data
    ONLINE->>+ONLINEDB: Write Features (Redis:6379/PostgreSQL:5432, TLS Optional)
    ONLINEDB-->>-ONLINE: Confirm
    ONLINE-->>-CRON: Materialization Complete

    Note over STREAM,OFFLINEDB: Flow 4: Feature Push (Streaming)
    STREAM->>+ONLINE: POST /push (HTTP:80, Bearer Token)
    ONLINE->>+ONLINEDB: Write Features (Redis:6379/PostgreSQL:5432, TLS Optional)
    ONLINEDB-->>-ONLINE: Confirm
    ONLINE->>+OFFLINEDB: Write to Offline (Optional, HTTPS:443, TLS 1.2+)
    OFFLINEDB-->>-ONLINE: Confirm
    ONLINE-->>-STREAM: Push Complete
